pathos: a framework for heterogeneous computing

Current release:
    pathos-0.1a1

Installation:
    $ python setup.py build
    $ python setup.py install

License:
    >>> print pathos.__license__

More information:
    http://www.cacr.caltech.edu/~mmckerns/



NOTE: The current implementation of pathos required slight modifications
to two external dependencies. These dependencies are provided in the
`pathos.external` directory for users installing without setuptools.

